{"tid":1165332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普稱中美協議必須更有利於美國，外交部回應","createTime":"2019-05-21T17:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T23:43:53.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b19908d80aa4b9b7b01887fded8fa8652b8dfa4","tid":1165332,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱中美協議必須更有利於美國，外交部回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OymHs04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOymHs04.jpg&h=974cb731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報導，美國總統特朗普近日接受媒體採訪時稱，最近幾輪美中磋商之前他曾經告訴中方，美中之間的協議不可能是&zwnj;&zwnj;對等的（50-50），由於中國過去的貿易做法，協議必須更有利於美國。中方對此有何回應？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陸慷：我不是貿易專家，但是我覺得有必要釐清&ldquo;是否對等&rdquo;和&ldquo;對誰更有利&rdquo;這兩個概念&zwnj;&zwnj;。 &zwnj;&zwnj;在貿易關係中這兩者不是一回事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求兩個經濟體在貿易實踐中絕對對等開放是不現實的，&zwnj;&zwnj;更何況經濟全球化本身就是各國優勢互補、互通有無的過程。我舉一個例子，&zwnj;&zwnj;2017年，中國對帶殼花生徵收的關稅是15%，&zwnj;&zwnj;而美國是163.8%。能簡單說美國占了便宜嗎？ &zwnj;&zwnj;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所謂貿易互惠互利，應該是指所有產業開放市場實現總體互惠和利益平衡。簡單認為美國在中美貿易關係中&ldquo;吃虧&rdquo;的看法是不科學、不專業的。所以，談判貿易協議本身，不可能在所有領域要求絕對的平等，但是協議必須是雙向平衡、平等互利的&zwnj;&zwnj;。"},{"pid":"9c45fb57e273268c2b3d7291fc533f9fc6ca7deb","tid":1165332,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"帶殼花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5396e612702e0f78025f7703dfbc291014fc6582","tid":1165332,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"駁不到了，中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d1bbb0d4bd3d68d9e010aafbd936b71d00a06c","tid":1165332,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T21:30:23.000Z","msg":"你o岩呀 所以偷你野係應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94257589c0f6f3352aaaf33c1ac8d1ba0fbce358","tid":1165332,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d1bbb0d4bd3d68d9e010aafbd936b71d00a06c","tid":1165332,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T21:30:23.000Z","msg":"你o岩呀 所以偷你野係應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}